caption:
There is something really therapeutic in creating a moment on set with someone who has never posed before: 
Helping them leave out the insecurity and building up their confidence. 
It takes a lot of energy as I truly give myself completely, over and over again, gaining the trust of such different women in a short amount of time.
Strangers allowing each other in.
These are my favorite encounters, 
true beauty in all kinds of age, shape, ethnicity.
